---
title: North African-Style Loaded Chicken Bowls with Roasted Sweet Potatoes
description: Get ready for explosions of flavour and colour with this hearty salad! Moroccan-spiced, roasted sweet potatoes and harissa-spiced onions bring depth and warmth to this weeknight wonder.
